
System Monitoring


   ServerApp - (Push and Pull server)

   PushClientApp - (placed to the monitored host)

   PullClientApp - (monitoring app)



  requirements:

	 - Java JDK (tested with java version 1.7, OpenJDK)
	 - MySQL


  external libraries used:

	google-gson (https://code.google.com/p/google-gson/)
	JDBC Driver for MySQL (http://dev.mysql.com/downloads/connector/j/)
	Sigar (https://support.hyperic.com/display/SIGAR/Home)




	(*) proof of concept stage
